        {
            "title": "梁茵反擊「交際花」指控：李佳芯一樣要硬食 拍短劇再做拜金女丨獨家",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"梁茵反擊「交際花」指控：李佳芯一樣要硬食 拍短劇再做拜金女。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/8ee8af289c07a58e93f888ef9fc91fd2/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250320/_2025032020541577591.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">梁茵反擊「交際花」指控：李佳芯一樣要硬食 拍短劇再做拜金女。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>曾在TVB《愛‧回家之開心速遞》演「威龍潘金蓮」Anita的梁茵（Kiko）拜金女形象深入民心，她在開電視短劇《我家有囍事》中再進擊有錢仔林德信，重提當年被指介入已婚富貴馬主律師的「第3者」，又誤為「交際花」 ，Kiko依然無奈解畫：「係配合喺舊公司要求，搵投資方爭取更多演出，狀況如李佳芯跟『蟲草大王』陳恩徳傳出緋聞一樣。」 採訪：方騫平 場地：Vibe Sea To Sky@觀塘鴻圖道\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"梁茵努力轉型從商求生存空間。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/49a071b0feada52d2edf191bc032582d/2025-03/4245.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        梁茵努力轉型從商求生存空間。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"梁茵承認演拜金女角色對她的確有影響。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7d8cc9d4291c41d05c4375b6b077169c/2025-03/4249.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        梁茵承認演拜金女角色對她的確有影響。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"梁茵當年被指係「交際花」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b840d10559f97f1e12197f7205324941/2025-03/4254.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        梁茵當年被指係「交際花」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"𠵱家學會放鬆心情。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f3f1682f31be5b8999ccd0cb4ef2a0b6/2025-03/4263.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        𠵱家學會放鬆心情。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"梁茵懂得為自己打算。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e4332cc8ecb96ff4e2738bcfe650d3a9/2025-03/LNN_4240.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        梁茵懂得為自己打算。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"提到往事仍耿耿於懷。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b143ce175405c72fb1be57742d9aa380/2025-03/LNN_4274.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        提到往事仍耿耿於懷。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>離開TVB 3年的梁茵，最近為首個開電視自家微短劇《我家有囍事》再做拜金女，迷惑富家公子林德信，成為林德信和林穎彤的「第3者」，enjoy演出的她說：「我着黑絲進攻，用意識形態嚟交代！」曾揚言不想再演拜金女的Kiko今次肯破例，她解釋道：「因為會加入啲狂嘢搞笑元素中和下，而且做反派、做醜角畀人記得多啲，反而比較優勝。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"開電視短劇中着黑絲色誘有錢仔林德信。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4c1912e4be4c9295f523a93e7265bd44/2025-03/78_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        開電視短劇中着黑絲色誘有錢仔林德信。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"主動向林德信出擊。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b2d1f3f1dd4c93e05dd6d618374e3282/2025-03/91_3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        主動向林德信出擊。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"梁茵亦步亦趨。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e4eb16a7f9132f3e8525161f7b2c146c/2025-03/92_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        梁茵亦步亦趨。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"《我家有囍事》中成為林德信及林穎彤的「第3者」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3259097c02fcf9d28b77d416d27d263b/2025-03/WNE03P01280225.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《我家有囍事》中成為林德信及林穎彤的「第3者」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"今期爆紅的七師傅也有份演出。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/96e47c5a004d117fda3bc37ad6eeeb12/2025-03/4_3_23.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        今期爆紅的七師傅也有份演出。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><strong>被街坊指住頭鬧</strong>(\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p>當年Kiko不忿「成也Anita敗也Anita」，她承認拜金女角色對她的確有影響，尤其觀眾好入戲，更自爆說：「試過出街時畀人指住個頭嚟鬧我『呢個係貪錢嘅衰人』感覺真係好難受，唯一自我安慰係演得好而受認同，也被標籤為拜金女、第3者。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Kiko大晒噴血惹火身材。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c5e0b725621cc7aa25240fa2e8b64c31/2025-03/03_31.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Kiko大晒噴血惹火身材。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"梁茵不時出海。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d198a72d2be77958742be5dbbc754799/2025-03/thumbnail_2__3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        梁茵不時出海。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"長腿美女。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4e003c46ccd5938f65e390b3a0c46bd1/2025-03/thumbnail_5.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        長腿美女。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"扮成學生妹。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/875cd93cabd5683df8ff3c7832d099ee/2025-03/thumbnail_1__6.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        扮成學生妹。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"梁茵有好豐滿身材。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4aa8a2f9dfcaf232c861a0bd4a5ebf5d/2025-03/thumbnail_7__4.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        梁茵有好豐滿身材。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"年前有報道指梁茵(Kiko)疑和一位富貴已婚律師兼馬主過從甚密。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d72738ac204a5a207d494f3a9aa1e19e/2025-03/Kiko_2021.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        年前有報道指梁茵(Kiko)疑和一位富貴已婚律師兼馬主過從甚密。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"梁茵曾參演電視劇集《金宵大廈》。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/204ce408421309feebfc9c85a6b9e86d/2025-03/Kiko_L_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        梁茵曾參演電視劇集《金宵大廈》。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"梁茵、陳睿雯晒身材。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/679cdaf79114fbc050ec904ef3d0e501/2025-03/174247199142946.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        梁茵、陳睿雯晒身材。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"梁茵「交際花」形象入型入格。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e816e15b46aaabf5d6c61dd47b824e33/2025-03/thumbnail_5__0_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        梁茵「交際花」形象入型入格。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"《愛‧回家之開心速遞》中演姣精「威龍潘金蓮」Anita。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b589811076879cc81ae9783e28c5ca3d/2025-03/thumbnail_8__3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《愛‧回家之開心速遞》中演姣精「威龍潘金蓮」Anita。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>重提當年被指係「交際花」，Kiko無奈梗食，一度耿耿於懷：「當年舊公司提出，搵到贊助嘅話就會有多啲演出機會，劇集篇幅都會多啲，既然有咁嘅機會自己都想搵投資方爭取下，互惠互利啫，點知畀人認定係別有用心嘅拜金女，就算澄清1千次都冇用，最慘連當時男朋友都存疑，追問我『約咗邊個監製導演？下期又搵個金主？船主、贊助商、高層.. 』.呢啲咁嘅負面消息由入行至今都未停過，我唯有做好自己，好彩得到家人支持。」最令她釋懷的，連一線花旦李佳芯都被人誤會：「與其改變唔到人哋諗法唯有改變自己。好彩𠵱家狀況好少少，啲人見我落舖(食店)做嘢，都好認真付出會改觀。」經此一役教她日後見客應酬時要保持距離，她好想求公平：「比如男士用安全手輕扶女仔條腰，呢啲舉動其實係觀點角度，如果發哥就講成幫手拉筋啫；吳彥祖就讚有紳士風度；但八両女變核突、肉酸。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"李佳芯跟「蟲草大王」陳恩徳傳過緋聞。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3e4229af3ed904502f932e07a80ac819/2025-03/4_143.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        李佳芯跟「蟲草大王」陳恩徳傳過緋聞。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"『蟲草大王』陳恩徳跟李佳芯慶生。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e4aa5f502cacf769605d95bb0c192ea7/2025-03/013_22.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        『蟲草大王』陳恩徳跟李佳芯慶生。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
